1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 9=

3
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:50,660
Wait for me.

4
00:00:51,780 --> 00:00:52,980
Wait for me to come back.

5
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:54,820
You have to wait for me.

6
00:00:56,420 --> 00:00:57,459
Yunqiu.

7
00:00:57,460 --> 00:00:58,099
Yunqiu.

8
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:59,060
Don't go.

9
00:01:02,380 --> 00:01:03,940
I'm so cold, Yunqiu.

10
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,420
(Why...)

11
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,660
(Why were you ruthless enough
to kill my entire family,)

12
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:12,980
(and yet still unable to let me go?)

13
00:01:15,660 --> 00:01:17,820
(Which one is the real you?)

14
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:19,620
The snow is falling so heavily.

15
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:24,620
I can't see you.

16
00:01:25,820 --> 00:01:27,979
I can't see where you are.

17
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:29,059
Where are you?

18
00:01:29,060 --> 00:01:30,020
Where are you?

19
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:31,100
Yunqiu.

20
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:33,460
Yunqiu, don't go.

21
00:01:34,540 --> 00:01:35,380
Don't go.

22
00:01:37,140 --> 00:01:40,379
ظآزJoy and pleasureظآز

23
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:45,859
ظآزCan you still see it within the night?ظآز

24
00:01:45,860 --> 00:01:52,260
ظآزThe life I long for
is tangled within itظآز

25
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:57,819
ظآزForcing me to trade pain for the pastظآز

26
00:01:57,820 --> 00:02:01,100
ظآزIn this worldظآز

27
00:03:03,700 --> 00:03:04,940
You're still burning up.

28
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,640
The doctor said you
need to take your medicine on time.

29
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:10,180
I'll go prepare the medicine.

30
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:38,900
Commander.

31
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:40,420
You're hurting me.

32
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:49,620
Does it hurt?

33
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:54,740
Isn't this exactly
how you like me to hold you?

34
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,380
Why are you awake?

35
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,500
You still have a fever.
The medicine will be ready soon.

36
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:04,300
I'm not that fragile.

37
00:04:06,100 --> 00:04:07,100
If you don't believe me,

38
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:08,780
see for yourself.

39
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:11,140
You haven't fully recovered yet.

40
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:12,540
You should go back first.

41
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:17,580
I'm fine now.

42
00:04:19,780 --> 00:04:20,780
See?

43
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,259
I'm better already.

44
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:23,820
If you don't believe me,
feel for yourself.

45
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:30,100
(It really doesn't feel hot anymore.)

46
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:33,300
See?

47
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,460
I'm fine.

48
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:39,220
It's just that my heart heats up

49
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:41,900
whenever I look at you.

50
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:44,540
I want you.

51
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,820
What exactly are you trying to do?

52
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:52,860
You should go back first.

53
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:06,780
Alright.

54
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:50,300
Wasn't your fever gone just now?

55
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,020
Why is it back again?

56
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:14,379
Just bear with it.

57
00:06:14,380 --> 00:06:15,580
It'll be ready soon.

58
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:34,600
ظآزWhat is there to seek or desire,
trapped in worldly sorrow?ظآز

59
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:41,040
ظآزEntangled through lifetimes,
drawn into chaos and schemesظآز

60
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:44,400
ظآزYour silhouetteظآز

61
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:47,440
ظآزCarved through endless hardshipظآز

62
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:53,440
ظآزLove and longing
traced through countless lifetimesظآز

63
00:06:54,200 --> 00:07:00,200
ظآزFates intertwined,
right and wrong no longer clearظآز

64
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,139
ظآزThe world becomes a prisonظآز

65
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:06,520
ظآزEven fleeting happiness is enoughظآز

66
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:09,279
ظآزThis heart and love slowly fade awayظآز

67
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:12,560
ظآزWhat ending will this fate become?ظآز

68
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,839
ظآزCrossing through
the barriers of dreamsظآز

69
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,639
ظآزBurning away all my devotionظآز

70
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:19,160
ظآزEngraving the promises we madeظآز

71
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:22,839
ظآزIf time has been wasted for too longظآز

72
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:25,720
ظآزHow can love remain so calm?ظآز

73
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:29,199
ظآزSo called blame,
nothing more than an excuseظآز

74
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:32,359
ظآزWhere in time did my heart belong?ظآز

75
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:35,519
ظآزEven if time has given up on usظآز

76
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:38,799
ظآزI still long to hold you once againظآز

77
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,999
ظآزWhen love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?ظآز

78
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:47,080
ظآزLet the frost wither
the greenery beyond the windowظآز

79
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:24,619
(This jade pendant...)

80
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:30,160
ظآزLove is so strange,
the way it entangles meظآز

81
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,220
(Zhuang Yunqiu...)

82
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,340
(Could it really be you?)

83
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:46,070
ظآزHow can broken love ever go on?ظآز

84
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:52,700
ظآزHow much hope must fade into despair?ظآز

85
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:56,780
ظآزIn the blink of an eye,
everything falls apartظآز

86
00:09:57,120 --> 00:10:00,130
ظآزBound by the fate we cannot escapeظآز

87
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:05,420
ظآزYou and I caught in
this tangled love and hateظآز

88
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:11,730
ظآزFragile hearts can hardly bear goodbyeظآز

89
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:18,390
ظآزHow many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?ظآز

90
00:10:18,930 --> 00:10:22,310
ظآزI once gave myself
to you so completelyظآز

91
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:25,509
ظآزStill holding on to that heartظآز

92
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:30,649
ظآزOnly to suffer your fatal blowظآز

93
00:10:30,650 --> 00:10:34,969
ظآزHow desperately
I long to hold you closeظآز

94
00:10:34,970 --> 00:10:37,549
ظآزYet I approach you with such cautionظآز

95
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:39,829
ظآزHow could a stand in ever haveظآز

96
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:43,379
ظآزThe right to be loved by you?ظآز

97
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:47,909
ظآزIf love is nothing
more than endless schemesظآز

98
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:50,440
ظآزUsed and abandoned in the endظآز

99
00:10:50,580 --> 00:10:52,529
ظآزStill I walk intoظآز

100
00:10:52,530 --> 00:10:56,129
ظآزThe trap you set without regretظآز

101
00:10:56,130 --> 00:11:00,179
ظآزHow desperately
I long to hold you closeظآز

102
00:11:00,180 --> 00:11:02,759
ظآزYet keep it buried deep insideظآز

103
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,919
ظآزA stand in can never crossظآز

104
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:08,359
ظآزThe shortest distance between usظآز

105
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:13,330
ظآزIf love can
make someone lose themselvesظآز

106
00:11:13,490 --> 00:11:18,160
ظآزThen let me stay by your sideظآز

107
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:22,509
ظآزA substituteظآز

108
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:27,510
ظآزNeeds no reasonظآز

